      "url": "https://www.instagram.com/reel/DVlmk_oAIPC/",
      "caption": "Part 2\n\nIn The Matrix, the red pill wasn’t about rebellion.\n\nIt was about awareness.\n\nThe moment Neo sees the system for what it is, everything changes.\n\nPsychology has a word for that moment: metacognition.\n\nThe ability to step back and observe your thoughts instead of automatically believing them.\n\nAnd when you start doing that, something powerful happens.\n\nYou realize some of the thoughts running your life…\n\nweren’t written by truth.\n\nThey were written by survival.\n\nBy fear.\nBy trauma.\nBy the brain trying to protect you.\n\nAwareness doesn’t erase the past.\n\nBut it breaks the illusion that those thoughts are your identity.\n\nAnd once you see the code…\n\nYou can’t go back to believing the program.\n\n#traumahealingjourney #metacognition #traumahealing #matrix #fyp"
