      "caption": "I Love PORTUGAL.\nI spent 3 weeks in this lovely phenomenal awesome incredible spirited RadCOUNTRY.\n\nEach of these 10 Photos have a profound effect on me and each has a story.\n\n1. The simplest of all the photos...is telling of my adventures in Portugal...it's just Strawberries but a side story is that I grew up in America next to Oxnard and Salinas at different times of my life...which are famous for their Strawberries and Fresh Produce and the strawberries that I had in Porto, Portugal where the sweetest fruit that my taste buds have ever tasted...I had a food orgasm ...of the deepest pleasures....this is PORTUGAL\n... pure, unconditional and POWERFUL.\n\nI was blessed to have the opportunity to travel and I sponged every moment that I could and took everything in....I am humbled and I'm motivated to be a better me and thankful for all the beautiful people that I met and the moments that we shared together.\n\nThank U PORTUGAL 🙌🌍🌎🙏💕✨🙌💕💕💕💕\n\nRadHUMANsOf the🌍✨🌎WORLD\n\n#illoveportugal #thankyouportugal #portugalambassador"
