      "caption": "“Camouflage tactics:\nThere are different types of camouflage, and some animals use more than one kind. One of the most common tactics is background matching. It could be as simple as a fox’s white fur matching the color of the Arctic tundra...” or Poliana’s outfit blending in with cliffs ☝️"
