      "caption": "I'm about to drop fire 👇\n\nThese are quick tips for improving your life and rebelling against modern norms that are killing you, depressing you, and sucking your soul dry.\n\nIn the next 30 days, you could:\n\n* Build a new habit\n* Learn the fundamentals of a new skill\n* Write an ebook\n* Fix your diet\n* Start a blog\n\nBut most people will use it for:\n* binge-watch Netflix\n* waste money on things they don't need\n* sleeping in every day\n\nRebel against this by focusing on your fundamentals.\n\nUnless you want to lose...\n\nSo to minimize failure...\n\nFocus on your fundamentals.\n\nTherefore:\nNever ignore your diet fundamentals.\nNever ignore your mindset fundamentals.\nNever ignore your financial fundamentals.\nNever ignore your relationship fundamentals.\n\nAs the fundamentals never change. \n\nAnd mastering them puts you ahead of the curve.\n\nWhile most people are focused on learning the \"modern\" methods that change every 7 days...\n\nYou focus on building up your life by rebelling against modern standards that are at an all-time low."
