      "url": "https://www.instagram.com/reel/CfrBmzpDxoT/",
      "caption": "Do you derive more pleasure from receiving or from giving? Pleasure gained does not last long before new pleasure is craved…\n\nWhy then do people in pursuit of pleasure believe that love will satisfy their needs? \n\nThe persistent need for pleasure is a trap of one’s own making.\n\nOne who seeks pleasure from others will indefinitely want more of it, while someone who already experiences the pleasure of life wants only to share in the experience with another to fall in love even more with themselves, the other, and the overall journey….\n\nPleasure is scarce, love is boundless. \n\n#thinkaboutit #pleasure #mindfulness #awakening #knowthyself #awaken #love #intention #mindset #relationships #pursuitofhappiness"
